<a_left_sidehead>Automatic Conversion</a_left_sidehead>
  <numbered_2_para><b>Automatic Conversion in a Qualified Financing.</b> If the Company issues Equity Securities in a Qualified Financing, then the Notes<? if (data._orig_interest != 0) { ?>, and any accrued but unpaid interest thereon,<? } ?> will automatically convert into the equity securities issued pursuant to the Qualified Financing at the Conversion Price.</numbered_2_para>
  <? if (iHaveCap) { ?>
  <numbered_2_para><b>Automatic Conversion at the Maturity Date.</b> If the Notes have not been previously converted pursuant to a Qualified Financing, then, effective upon the Maturity Date, the Notes, and any accrued but unpaid interest thereon, will automatically convert into Equity Securities at <?= (100 - data.maturity_conversion_discount).toFixed(2) ?>% of the Valuation Cap.</numbered_2_para>
<?}?>

  <? if (iHaveCap) { ?>
  <a_left_sidehead>Optional Conversion</a_left_sidehead>
  <numbered_2_para>If the Maturity Date or a Qualified Financing has not occurred, the Investor may elect to convert the entire Investment Amount into Equity Securities at the Valuation Cap.</numbered_2_para>
<?}?>


  <a_left_sidehead>Sale of the Company</a_left_sidehead>
  <numbered_2_para>If a Qualified Financing has not occurred and the Company elects to consummate a sale of the Company prior to the Maturity Date, then at the election of the Investor, <? if (iHaveCap) { ?>either</numbered_2_para>
  <numbered_3_para><?}?>the Investor shall receive a payment equal to <?= data.acquisition_preference ?> times the Notes<? if (iHaveCap) { ?>, or</numbered_3_para>
  <numbered_3_para>the entire Investment Amount shall convert into Equity Securities at the Valuation Cap.</numbered_3_para><? } else { ?>.</numbered_2_para><?}?>


  <a_left_sidehead>Pre-Payment</a_left_sidehead>
  <numbered_2_para>The Note may not be prepaid unless approved in writing by Investors holding Notes whose aggregate principal amount represents a majority of the outstanding principal amount of all then-outstanding Notes (the &#8220;<b>Requisite Holders</b>&#8221;).</numbered_2_para>



  <a_left_sidehead>Participation Right</a_left_sidehead>
  <numbered_2_para>The Investor will have the right to participate in future financing rounds of the Company in order to maintain their percentage shareholding in the Company, calculated on fully-diluted basis.
When a Qualified Financing triggers conversion of the Note to Equity Securities, the Investor will have the right to participate in that Qualified Financing.
Should the Company issue equity securities or securities convertible to equity, subsequent to the current Series, but prior to the Qualified Financing, the Company shall give the Investor notice of the terms of that financing, and the Investor shall possess the right to participate in that financing on a pro rata basis.</numbered_2_para>

  <a_left_sidehead>Amendment and Waiver</a_left_sidehead>
  <numbered_2_para>The terms of this Agreement and the Notes may be amended, or any term thereof waived, upon the written consent of the Company and the Requisite Holders.</numbered_2_para>


  <a_left_sidehead>No Security Interest</a_left_sidehead>
  <numbered_2_para>The Notes will be a general unsecured obligation of the Company.</numbered_2_para>


